text: And the Lord said to Aaron, Thou and thy sons and thy father's house with thee shall bear the iniquity of the sanctuary, and Thou and thy sons with thee shall bear the sins of your priesthood. Thou and thy father's house with thee shall bear the iniquity of the ayah.
